element.name: Julskatten by kimitski, Traditional Cache (2/2)
element.description: The cache is among a pile of stones above the wall at the rise along the Cliff Walk of Bray Head.
element.long-description:
The cache is a white plastic tupe ca 1.5 liter.
Start-Up Contents: T.B. The holy grail. Heartshaped soap. Eye pen A spinning man Eye-protecter Cereal-Box-Man Santa Claus candle EU Badge 2 Ghost cards 1 Logbook 1 Key holder 6 Plastic stones Coins A poem. (“A Trail of Choice” By Karl Byrne)
